text.tspan: CodeDay is a creative and fun program
At CodeDay, students pitch their own ideas for apps or games, then
work with other students to make them a reality over a weekend.
Our background-checked staff and industry mentors help students
along the way, with introductory-level workshops and 1-1 mentoring.
Since 2011, we’ve run more than 350 CodeDays in 49 cities worldwide,
Middle school, high school, and college undergrads.
